aris\"}, {\"begin\": 1700, \"end\": 1707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reginald_of_Sidon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.518985615877326e-13, \"text\": \"Raynald\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reginald_of_Sidon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reginald_of_Sidon\"}, {\"begin\": 1721, \"end\": 1726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.429657487641578e-16, \"text\": \"Omega\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am also delighted to share the moment with Nicole, who always styles our timepieces in such a captivating way.\\\"\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kidman joined Omega as a brand ambassador in 2005 and has been a longtime supporter of the Swiss luxury brand ever since.\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1920, \"end\": 1925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.429657487641578e-16, \"text\": \"Omega\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\"}, {\"begin\": 1997, \"end\": 2002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swiss_made\", \"score\": 0.9999904269547021, \"rank\": 9.56393857068668e-06, \"text\": \"Swiss\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swiss_made\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swiss_made\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always loved working with Omega because of the versatility of the brand,\\\" she said in a statement.\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2062, \"end\": 2067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.429657487641578