ann reflected on their longstanding relationship.\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2437, \"end\": 2440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_Wear_Daily\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WWD\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_Wear_Daily\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_Wear_Daily\"}, {\"begin\": 2442, \"end\": 2447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.429657487641578e-16, \"text\": \"Omega\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omega_SA\"}, {\"begin\": 2466, \"end\": 2473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reginald_of_Sidon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.518985615877326e-13, \"text\": \"Raynald\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reginald_of_Sidon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reginald_of_Sidon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When we look for ambassadors, we look for people that are not just around one day, one year or two years - the biggest of the biggest people that have a lot of character, determination and devotion to their profession and bring a lot to us,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because of this continuity in our values, it's quite rare to find people like her or like George Clooney, who have been so many years doing their job in an excellent way.\\u2026And that's why we like being connected to some people like that because they are our heroes.\\\"\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 3049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2875, \"end\": 2889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Clooney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"George Clooney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"